      "name": "toasted sesame seeds",
      "amount": "1 tablespoon"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to medium-high heat, about 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together soy sauce, brown sugar, garlic, and ginger to make the marinade.",
    "Add the pancetta slices to the marinade and mix well to coat.",
    "Thread the marinated pancetta slices onto skewers, leaving a small space between each slice.",
    "Brush the grill with sesame oil to prevent sticking.",
    "Grill the pancetta skewers for 2-3 minutes per side, or until crispy and golden brown.",
    "Garnish with green onions and toasted sesame seeds.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
  ],
